ygData.messageBody:
well i'm a long time reader first time writer :) I have to agree with the
last statement by Cristie. I don't care if people twink, don't get me wrong
it pisses me off, but i really don't care. What i really hate is the guild
camping. I don't want to join a guild but it seems i might have to just to
get the good equipment. I think that's more of a problem then twinking. I
say leave twinking alone and concentrate on stuff that could really affect
you. just my 2 cents!!!

Parthon lvl 12
Solosek Ro
